{#
  funding.njk — disclosure panel for "How We're Funded". Opened by the
  matching tip-badge button in the article-header__support-row. Hidden
  by default; the support-row button toggles [hidden] + aria-expanded.
#}
{% set fundAuthor = authors[author] if author and authors[author] else null %}
{% set authorTipUrl = fundAuthor.tipping.kofi or fundAuthor.tipping.bmac or fundAuthor.tipping.patreon if fundAuthor else null %}
{% set pubTipUrl = site.tipping.kofi or site.tipping.bmac or site.tipping.patreon %}
<div id="funding-panel" class="funding funding--panel" hidden aria-labelledby="funding-heading">
  <div class="funding__body">
    <p class="funding__kicker">No ads. No sponsors. No paywalls.</p>
    <h2 id="funding-heading" class="funding__heading">Funded entirely by readers</h2>
    <p class="funding__lede">
      {{ site.title }} runs on direct reader contributions, not advertising or platform deals. Tips go to the publication&rsquo;s operating costs (hosting, FOIA fees, the occasional travel for reporting) or directly to the writer of an individual piece. We take no money from advertisers, sponsors, partner networks, or syndication platforms.
    </p>

    <ul class="funding__bullets">
      <li><strong>What your support pays for:</strong> hosting and infrastructure, contributor honoraria, public-records requests, and a minimal editorial budget. Itemised on the <a href="/costs/">costs page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>What it doesn&rsquo;t pay for:</strong> ads, sponsorships, native content, tracking pixels, paywalls, or syndication-network fees. There are none.</li>
      <li><strong>Editorial independence:</strong> contributors are paid the same regardless of how a piece performs. We don&rsquo;t track per-article tip totals to set rates. Editorial decisions are not influenced by individual reader contributions.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="funding__actions">
      {% if authorTipUrl and fundAuthor.name %}
      <a class="funding__action funding__action--primary" href="{{ authorTipUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-umami-event="support-author">
        Support {{ fundAuthor.name }}
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% if pubTipUrl %}
      <a class="funding__action" href="{{ pubTipUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-umami-event="support-publication">
        Support {{ site.title }}
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      <a class="funding__action funding__action--ghost" href="/support/" data-umami-event="support-learn">
        Read the full disclosure &rsaquo;
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
